        <article class="article-content">
          <div class="article-intro">
            <p class="lead">You just got your Airbnb listing live. Now comes the question every GTA host faces: <strong>should you manage it yourself, or hire a property manager?</strong> The answer depends on your time, your revenue goals, and how you feel about 2 AM guest messages. Here's the honest breakdown with real numbers from the Toronto market.</p>
