          <h2 id="time-cost">The Real Time Cost of Self-Managing an Airbnb</h2>
          <p>Most new hosts underestimate how much time self-managing actually takes. It's not just "answering a few messages." Here's a realistic breakdown of the weekly time commitment for a single active listing.</p>

